{"tid":389853,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】少年，燃燒你的熱血吧!!! 棒球之龍6 Day109 6/9","createTime":"2017-09-06T15:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T19:02:53.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9566e9c2bee124b795757ca852e5420c847d4b","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=uWhpOTAvkXPwREn6UIw4dCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0504adb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，開台前或者有任何突發事唔開都會Po上FB。<br />\n有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=uWhpOTAvkXPwREn6UIw4dCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=be9fc743\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NRSeWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNRSeWz.jpg&h=f4a261d8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我亦開左個Youtuber Page放開台嘅Backup<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg&d=uWhpOTAvkXPwREn6UIw4dCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=0318620f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCa49ivSXtdCYwObEq9pRLSg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">請各位多多支持，比D錢黎洗下</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"f166d235e4407b4a4f3fc4c335fa05cac382c00c","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27ff79ac86c0a40cd84b892aea021cc89289880","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aadb4eaffeb75a9745979df1559cfdcd05dfbed","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87fb9a2e9aed26042b5603526b3c2fd831a5050","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ece590b1cb76b33f49a412c99e3d49944f9befe","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe1a575a7681d73afcf60e260a9311be557015d9","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de89686ccda90e5c767d8e3180dee1af64669125","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:28:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbd468f6bb2ad126697df448349d5734fb73b99","tid":389853,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\